### CardAction . update_func
``` lua
local card_action	-- example card_action
local function on_update( self, time )
  print( "CardAction updating." )
end

card_action.update_func = on_update
```

Assigns a **`function`** that will be executed every frame that this <%= @link_card_action %> **is active**.

#### Variable Type
**`function`**

#### Assignment
`<%= @variable_text %>.update_func = on_update`

#### Parameters
**`function`** `on_update`<br>
	&emsp;_The **`function`** you want this to execute when the <%= @link_card_action %> completes._

``` lua
local function update_func( self, time )
end
```
<aside class="notice"><code>attack_func</code> requires <b>one</b> <%= @link_card_action %> parameter, <b>one</b> **`number`** parameter, and to return <b>nothing</b>.<br>
The <code>self</code> parameter will be passed a reference to itself.<br>
The <code>time</code> parameter will be passed the *elapsed time* since the last time it was executed.</aside>
